ZH: 小猫很调皮，经常捣乱。
EN: The kitten is very naughty and always causing trouble.

ZH: 孩子们调皮地嬉戏在花园里。
EN: The children playfully romp in the garden.

ZH: 她有一种调皮生动的个性。
EN: She has a playful and lively personality.

ZH: 我的弟弟总是调皮捣蛋。
EN: My little brother is always mischievous.

